{
  "stem": "13469.7",
  "chunk_idx": 7,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 4.1,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "[NON-ENGLISH] remembers that, in particular.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "We threw all their stuff out of the window, kind of thing, and, and--",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I don't know about what.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Maybe about chewing gum, or God knows what-- something.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "[LAUGHS] But we remember, there was, in particular, three boys-- the [NON-ENGLISH] or [NON-ENGLISH] or whatever they were called.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Three of them-- they'd lost their parents, and they finished up in Israel later.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "They were big mates of ours, but we always had rows-- us two against them three.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And, and [NON-ENGLISH] remembers very well that one day, we were on the second floor or third floor or something, and we threw all their stuff out of the window one day.",
      "word_count": 32
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "The Americans got very angry at us about it.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "But we stayed in Leipzig for several days while they try and sort it out who was who.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And then they said, yes, you can go back to Holland.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And they made up a transport of people to go back to Holland, Belgium, and France-- of camp survivors, kind of thing.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "And it was when we went out of this camp, in Leipzig, on an open truck, another open truck came into the camp.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "And on this other open truck was our sister, Eve.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "And, and basically, as I said, we'd forgotten all about her, really.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "It was very bad, considering she was the only reason why we survived.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "If it hadn't been for her, we'd have been in Sobibor or Auschwitz.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "So it was very bad of us to have forgotten about her.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "But let me just say that we were busy trying to survive ourselves.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "And, and we just forgot about her.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "We didn't really know how or what we could have done, actually, to try and find her.",
      "word_count": 17
    }
  ],
